                     <span class="l">Soon shall thy arm, U<span class="smallcaps">nconquer&#x02BC;d</span> S<span class="smallcaps">team</span>! afar</span><br/>
                     <span class="l">Drag the slow barge, or drive the rapid car;</span><br/>
                     <span class="l">Or on wide&#x2010;waving wings expanded bear</span><br/>
